cted persons said the kidnappers were yet to make contact with them as at press time, but it was learned Governor Ifeanyi Ugwuanyi had ordered for combing of surrounding bushes in the area. State Police Public Relations Officer, Daniel Ndukwe, could not pick his calls nor react to a text message sent to him on the matter. Vanguard TWO men were on Friday evening abducted by gunmen, suspected to be Herdsmen along Ugwogo-Isi-Uzo road and taken to an unknown destination. August 1, 2020 In "News" The police have discovered a shallow grave where the remains of the former Chief Security Officer for Uzo-Uwani Local Government Area of Enugu State, Mr Ejiofor Enechi, were buried after being killed by his kidnappers. March 25, 2017 In "Crime Guard" Nimbo, a serene community in Uzo-Uwani L.G.A, Enugu state is in the news again, barely two years after it captured headlines nationally and internationally following a bloody massacre by Fulani herdsmen. February 25, 2017 In "Crime Guard"